Ans.10 = Keywords are some predefined and reserved words in python that have special meanings.
 Keywords are used to define the syntax of the coding. The keyword cannot be used as an
 identifier, function, and variable name. All the keywords in python are written in lower case 
 except True and False.

Ans.11 = Keywords are used to define the syntax of the coding. The keyword cannot be used as 
 an identifier, function, and variable name . keyword is the part of syntax in programming that
 have special meaning to the compiler so thats the reason we cannot use the keyword as a variable
 if we use a keyword as a variable our code will not run ,code will show an error. 

